Rediscover Othello
==========

HTML5 Othello/Reversi game.

Roadmap:

* Add more game modes
* Improve AI
* Make AI async
* Beautify code
* Reset preferences
* If #columns is very different than #rows, it doesn't look good
* Bug when changing color of multiple pieces (maybe audio bug?)
* Make walls
* Campaign
    * Show current #level
    * Allow playing previous levels
    * Show results from previous levels

Finished:
* Preferences
    * Choose color
* Allow odd number of cells
* Allow different number of rows and columns
* 'tableColor' -> 'boardColor'
* Best scores
* Allow starting in a different position
* Load maps from file
